articles.title: Tour de France team consider legal action after fan causes crash - The Guardian
articles.description: Jumbo-Visma, the team of Tour de France leader Jonas Vingegaard, are considering pressing charges after a fan caused a massive crash during the 15th stage
articles.content:
The team of the Tour de France leader, Jonas Vingegaard, are considering pressing charges after a spectator caused a massive crash during the 15th stage to Saint-Gervais Mont-Blanc on Sunday.
